dcterms:description: A self-driving car simulator that is a complex environment consisting of multiple immediate turns, making navigation challenging. It includes various objects like houses, trees, etc., resulting in a large variance in the observations from the environment.
dcterms:title: Duckietown self-driving car simulator

dcterms:description: A top-down shooting game where the goal is to maneuver a plane to destroy or avoid obstacles while continuously moving forward, all the while not crashing into the walls on the sides or the obstacles themselves.
dcterms:title: Atari River Raid environment

dcterms:description: A custom environment developed by the authors for 3D navigation tasks, designed to test the proposed reinforcement learning algorithm.
dcterms:title: 3D navigation environment
